data.description: This gorgeous, end-unit townhome has over 2300 SF of comfortable living space! Start with the main floor living room or office, and a large great room with a cozy fireplace, wood floors, wainscoting and molding. The kitchen features contemporary finishes to appeal to today's modern preferences, with lots of storage, granite, and tile backsplash. Transition outdoors to a covered patio and covered deck for all of your entertainment and relaxation needs. Upper level has a spacious primary BR with trey ceiling and closet with built-ins. The bath features granite countertops, garden tub, dual vanities and walk-in shower. 2 additional BRs, another full bath, and laundry complete the upper level. But wait, there’s more! The lower floor boasts a 4th bedroom and full bathroom.  Within walking distance of the optional amenities offered in the community. Very convenient to shopping, fine dining and interstates.
